  "texts": [
    "(4) NPA (Wu et al. 2019b): A personalized attention-based model that adaptively selects informative words and news based on individual user interests.",
    "(5) NAML (Wu et al. 2019a): A multi-view learning framework that jointly models title, abstract, and category information with attentive pooling.",
    "(6) LSTUR (An et al. 2019): A model that distinguishes short-and long-term user interests using GRUs and user embeddings.",
    "(7) NRMS (Wu et al. 2019c): A self-attention-based model that captures sequential user preferences and contextual dependencies between news.",
    "(8) HiFiArk (Liu et al. 2019): A hierarchical architecture that models fine-grained user preferences across subtopic and topic levels."
  ],
